##1. Create a greeting for your program.

print("Welcome to my generator")

##2. Ask the user to describe their personality in 3 words.

personality = input("Describe your personality in 3 words: \n") ##\n allows for a new line to be created

##3. Ask the user for their horoscope.

horoscope = input("What is your horoscope: \n") ##name the function personality and horoscope to use in next step

##4. Combine the name of their city and pet and show them their band name.
print(horoscope + " are " + personality) ##giving 'are' the proper space will read the sentence clearly

##this project shows understanding of print, input, line separation, concat, and using variables
